# Visual Drift Connect CRM Environment Configuration

# ==============================================================================
# Google OAuth 2.0 Credentials
# ==============================================================================
# Obtain these credentials from the Google Cloud Console:
# https://console.cloud.google.com
# 
# Steps to set up:
# 1. Create a project in Google Cloud Console.
# 2. Go to APIs & Services > OAuth consent screen. Set up OAuth consent.
# 3. Go to Credentials > Create Credentials > OAuth client ID.
# 4. Set Application Type to "Web application".
# 5. In "Authorized redirect URIs", add:
#    http://localhost:3000/api/integrations/google/callback
# 6. Copy the Client ID and Client Secret and paste them below.
#
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret_here

# ==============================================================================
# Resend Email Integration (Optional)
# ==============================================================================
# Obtain your API key from Resend (https://resend.com) to trigger email reminders.
#
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here
